Monday, November 07, 2005
GGGRRRRRR,..........!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!
Current mood: pissed off
I forgot to let everyone know I quit my job at Victoria's Secret. They said they suspected me of "causing losses to their company." -Which by the way is bullshit! I was 'by the book' on EVERYTHING!!!!!! I got so fed up in that office that I handed the Loss Prevention lady back my keys and walked out. GO ME! STICKIN' IT TO THE MAN! I already have another job if I want it, and it's so much more money$$$$$. I'm going to be making more money than my old bosses at VS. Success is definately the sweetest revenge. ASSHOLES!!!!!
10:01 AM - 0 Comments - 0 Kudos - Add Comment
Slightly Stoopid, BOH?!?
Current mood: okay
I SAW SLIGHTLY STOOPID LAST NIGHT!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!! IT WAS DA SHIT!!!!!! BOH! (credit to Will for the use of 'BOH!' because if I didn't give credit he'd say I copied him.) BOH! THE SHOW WAS AWESOME! Pictures will be coming soon. Stay tuned,..... BOH!
